# RocketRide IDE cloud-test ground — environment variables
# Copy the vars you have keys for into .env (the extension manages ROCKETRIDE_URI + ROCKETRIDE_APIKEY).
# Only ROCKETRIDE_* vars are substituted by the engine. Leave unused ones blank.

